      "observed_in": "Floors 5 and 15, Act 1 (fought twice) -- base attack opens at 3, a single Buff turn granted +7 Strength (confirmed via STRENGTH_POWER amount:7 in game state), and the next attack card showed as 11 total (base 4 + 7 Strength), matching the shared Strength-scaling formula."
